                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6036" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0916</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9126 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">藏器而动，乘时乘势：厦钨新能分拆上市“赶考”科创板</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">XTC New Energy Materials Spin off And Listing &quot;Catch up with The Examination&quot; Science And Innovation Board</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汪金祥，黄之莎，蔡世霖，陈龙飞，余雪娇，郑静凡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">厦门厦钨新能源材料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">厦钨新能；分拆上市；股东财富效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">XTC New Energy Materials; Spin off listing; Shareholder wealth effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年中国证监会发布的分拆上市政策新规席卷而来，打破了多年来中国资本市场上优质公司旗下的资本运作举步维艰的现状，与以往证监会传递的对分拆上市的“不鼓励”、“从严谨慎”的态度形成鲜明对比，这为上市企业提供了新的发展机会和融资渠道。本案例以2021年8月5日福建省首家“A拆A”成功的国有企业厦钨新能为例，以厦钨新能分拆上市的过程为主线，重点介绍其分拆的动因、股东财富效应、潜在风险与一般经验等。学生通过对本案例的学习与探讨，能够深入理解分拆上市的核心含义、企业分拆上市的动因和经济后果、以及企业分拆上市的价值创造效果，进一步提高理论与实践相结合的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2019, the new regulations on spin off and listing policies issued by China Securities Regulatory Commission swept through, breaking the current situation of difficult capital operation of high-quality companies in China&#39;s capital market for many years, in sharp contrast to the previous attitude of &quot;not encouraging&quot; and &quot;being strict and cautious&quot; on spin off and listing transmitted by China Securities Regulatory Commission, which provides new development opportunities and financing channels for listed enterprises. This case takes XTC New Energy Materials, the first state-owned enterprise in Fujian Province to successfully &quot;dismantle a&quot; on August 5, 2021 as an example,, and taking the process of XTC New Energy Materials&#39;s spin off and listing as the main line, this case focuses on the motivation of its spin off, shareholder wealth effect, potential risks and general experience. Through the study and discussion of this case, students can deeply understand the core meaning of spin off listing, the motivation and economic consequences of enterprise spin off listing, as well as the value creation effect of enterprise spin off listing, and further improve their ability to combine theory with practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《公司理财》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分拆上市</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
